column5: Has anyone been to the Big Whiteshell of late that can report on whether the ice is out and if it is out on surrounding lakes.
Was out in the southern Whiteshell on the weekend and its still iced over. Should be off over this weekend.
Talked to Bill, (Crowduck Lake Camp), and he indicated that there is still ice cover, and he had some reservations about the lake being clear for fishing season "Opening Day"
